Fieldmaps Nextflow Pipeline
==============================

Run the FieldMaps preprocessing pipeline on Datman subjects

USAGE

nextflow run fieldmaps.nf [options...] --study STUDY --out OUTDIR

DESCRIPTION
	--study		Datman study ID
	--out		Output directory

OPTIONAL
	--rewrite	Overwrite existing subject output directories
			($rewrite)
	--echo1		Echo 1 Datman Tag
			($echo1)
	--echo2		Echo 2 Datman Tag
			($echo2)
	--help		Print this usage log

SUPPORTED PROFILES
	-profile kimel	Run on Kimel cluster
	-profile scc	Run on SCC cluster
	-profile local	Run on local cluster

NOTES
Will automatically downsample if one ECHO map has a higher resolution than another
